<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="nowadays-adv">nowadays <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'naʊədeɪz/    美 /'naʊədeɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(与过去相比) 如今；现在：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nowadays people separate their waste to make it easier for it to be reused. 
现在人们把垃圾分类，以便于废物再利用。</p><footer> 2009 湖南改</footer></div></div>